            <title><![CDATA[【#8小时睡眠或许并非人类本能#[困]】每天一定要睡够8小时吗[疑问]？专家提醒，睡眠时长因人而异。有三种睡眠的类型：普通型每天睡6-8小时；短睡型每天睡4-5小时...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%238%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E6%88%96%E8%AE%B8%E5%B9%B6%E9%9D%9E%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E6%9C%AC%E8%83%BD%23&amp;extparam=%238%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E6%88%96%E8%AE%B8%E5%B9%B6%E9%9D%9E%E4%BA%BA%E7%B1%BB%E6%9C%AC%E8%83%BD%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#8小时睡眠或许并非人类本能#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[困]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_kun-0f87c3e1f8.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】每天一定要睡够8小时吗<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>？专家提醒，睡眠时长因人而异。有三种睡眠的类型：普通型每天睡6-8小时；短睡型每天睡4-5小时第二天就精力充沛；长睡型每天睡9小时以上才能解乏；多数成年人每天睡6-8小时就足够了，太在意睡眠时长，反而会让人焦虑，导致睡不好👇🏻（央视网） <a href="http://t.cn/A6NuGxNz" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
