            <title><![CDATA[【[可怜]#经常涂润唇膏会有副作用吗# 】最近气候干燥，嘴唇容易干燥起皮，专家分享#嘴唇起皮的3个护理方法# ①多喝水，保证皮肤、身体不缺水；②注意保湿，使用...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[可怜]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_kelian-a9df4278bf.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E6%B6%82%E6%B6%A6%E5%94%87%E8%86%8F%E4%BC%9A%E6%9C%89%E5%89%AF%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E6%B6%82%E6%B6%A6%E5%94%87%E8%86%8F%E4%BC%9A%E6%9C%89%E5%89%AF%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#经常涂润唇膏会有副作用吗#</span></a> 】最近气候干燥，嘴唇容易干燥起皮，专家分享<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%98%B4%E5%94%87%E8%B5%B7%E7%9A%AE%E7%9A%843%E4%B8%AA%E6%8A%A4%E7%90%86%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%98%B4%E5%94%87%E8%B5%B7%E7%9A%AE%E7%9A%843%E4%B8%AA%E6%8A%A4%E7%90%86%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#嘴唇起皮的3个护理方法#</span></a>  ①多喝水，保证皮肤、身体不缺水；②注意保湿，使用滋润一些的润唇膏来进行嘴唇保湿；③多吃水果、蔬菜，减少过辣、过咸、油腻食物的摄入👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（CCTV生活圈） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4969417730359322" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hjz6v54oqcj21hc0u0aeo.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/riD1h01Olx08agzgAMTe01041200bmjX0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1700469102&amp;ssig=38%2FSRcXmN5&amp;KID=unistor